<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sistem Informasi Akademik - B16</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@basecoat/basecoat/dist/basecoat.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --unand-green: #006837;
            --unand-yellow: #f9ed32;
        }
        body { 
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: var(--unand-green);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--unand-yellow);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1rem; }
        .grid-menu {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .menu-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .menu-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--unand-green); }
        .btn-unand {
            background-color: var(--unand-green);
            color: white !important;
            display: block;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .stat-badge {
            background: #e6f4ea;
            color: var(--unand-green);
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <div>
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">Sistem Pengajuan & Persetujuan SK</h1>
                <p style="margin: 0; opacity: 0.9;">Kelompok B16</p>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: right;">
                <span style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px;">Total Berkas Sistem: <b><%= stats.total %></b></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-left: 6px solid var(--unand-green); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: var(--unand-green);">Portal Manajemen Alur Dokumen</h2>
            <p>Silakan pilih panel akses Anda di bawah ini untuk memproses permohonan, menyetujui dokumen, dan menerbitkan Surat Keputusan (SK) resmi.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-menu">
            <div class="menu-card" style="border-top: 4px solid #0056b3;">
                <h3 style="color: #0056b3; margin-top:0;">Panel Kaprodi</h3>
                <p>Fitur untuk meninjau dan memberikan catatan rekomendasi tingkat prodi.</p>
                <div style="margin: 1rem 0;">Antrean Saat Ini: <span class="stat-badge"><%= stats.kaprodi %></span></div>
                <a href="/b16/kaprodi" class="btn-unand" style="background: #0056b3;">Buka Inbox Kaprodi</a>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-card" style="border-top: 4px solid var(--unand-yellow);">
                <h3 style="color: #856404; margin-top:0;">Panel Wakil Dekan 1</h3>
                <p>Fitur pengesahan akhir dan penerbitan nomor Surat Keputusan (SK).</p>
                <div style="margin: 1rem 0;">Menunggu Pengesahan: <span class="stat-badge" style="background:#fff3cd; color:#856404;"><%= stats.wd1 %></span></div>
                <a href="/b16/wd1" class="btn-unand" style="background: #d39e00; color: #fff !important;">Buka Inbox WD1</a>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-card" style="border-top: 4px solid #333;">
                <h3 style="color: #333; margin-top:0;">Radar Pelacakan</h3>
                <p>Mesin pencari global terintegrasi untuk melacak status dokumen pemohon.</p>
                <div style="margin: 1rem 0; visibility: hidden;">Spacer</div>
                <a href="/b16/radar" class="btn-unand" style="background: #333;">Buka Radar Global</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>